movie.title: Santet
movie.description_intro: A man and his family return home to see his ailing mother only to find out that she has been overcome by black magic.
movie.description_full: A man and his family return home to see his ailing mother only to find out that she has been overcome by black magic.

movies.title: Rock, Paper, Scissors
movies.summary: Peter "the Doll Maker" Harris returns to his ancestral family home after being released from the state's hospital for the criminally insane - a "cured" man. Once inside the old house, anguished memories from a tortured childhood and ghostly visitations from his past victims shake Peter's resolve. It isn't until lovely young Ashley enters his life that Peter makes a fateful decision, a decision that will rekindle old desires that always ended in murder.

movies.title: The Corpse Vanishes
movies.summary: Dr. Lorenz, a mad scientist, wants to keep his elderly wife young. He does this by kidnapping young females and extracting fluid from them. He then injects this fluid into his wife.

movies.title: If Footmen Tire You What Will Horses Do?
movies.title_english: If Footmen Tire You What Will Horses Do?
movies.title_long: If Footmen Tire You What Will Horses Do? (1971)
movies.summary: Based on the preachings of Reverend Estus W. Pirkle, this film warns what will happen to America if the citizens do not give up their depraved ways and turn to God and Jesus for salvation. Communist infiltrators, the "footmen," will pave the way for an all-out invasion by weakening our will through TV, dance, rock music, and alcohol. Once the invasion begins, the new Communist government will proceed to round up all Christians, and either execute them or force them to undergo re-education. Only by putting their faith in the Bible where it belongs, says Reverend Pirkle, can America resist the coming Red Menace.

movies.title: Ill: Final Contagium
movies.summary: Follow a mad Chilean scientist's deadly virus escape the lab on contaminated currency worldwide: a thief steals contaminated notes in Italy; a Kosovo patient is infected in extreme surgeries; a German father is desperate to save his son.
